title: SpaceX launches Starlink satellites from California on 160th Falcon 9 flight of the year (video)
description: A SpaceX Falcon 9 rocket carrying 27 Starlink satellites launched from Vandenberg Space Force Station in California on Dec. 10, 2025. It was the 160th Falcon 9 flight of the year.
